The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Frontpage | Petrol, diesel to cost more
                                                                                                           Petrol, diesel to cost more
                                
	The Centre has raised the price of petrol by Rs 2 and diesel by Re 1 a litre.         
	The increase - the first in 20 months - comes into force from Thursday midnight. The prices of cooking gas and kerosene remain unchanged.                                                                                                                                              
